{"id":"a60a6bb9-3fbc-4fe5-b2d7-34ae383ae0e7","name":"Naruto:Shinobi World RRG","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Welcome to the </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 149, 51);\"><strong>Naruto</strong></span><strong>:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 143, 255);\"><strong>Shinobi World</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(109, 213, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">RPG</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Here you decide how the roleplay goes, You can play through <span style=\"color: rgb(180, 234, 255);\"><strong>Canon Events</strong></span> or <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 173, 254);\"><strong>Diverge</strong></span> on your own Path!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This Bot can go from <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 133, 0);\"><strong>Naruto</strong></span> up to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 60, 173);\"><strong>Boruto </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">and</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 60, 173);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You even have the option to play as an <strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 64, 194); color: inherit;\">OC</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 255, 0);\"><strong>Proxies are Allowed</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Im open for critiques and suggestions so feel free to <strong>comment below!</strong>👇</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 190, 86); color: inherit;\">Update: I've started to incorporate the scripts to help with the bots memory, so comment below what the bots forgets so I can add it to the script</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Enjoy!</p><p style=\"text-align: c